    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FIND A GUN AND GET SOME MEAT! THE TRAIN IS HUNGRY..</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find yourself in a wasteland full of zombies, monsters and machines that all want you dead. <br>You start with only a melee weapon and an oxygen tank to help you breathe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Scavenge the world for weapons, ammo, scrap and upgrades.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216230/extras/d6413911c68db469df9545b2271ff50c.poster.avif?t=1771320063\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216230/extras/d6413911c68db469df9545b2271ff50c.webm?t=1771320063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216230/extras/d6413911c68db469df9545b2271ff50c.mp4?t=1771320063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The key to your survival is <strong>MEAT!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The <strong>MEAT TRAIN</strong> is your only hope of surviving, especially when the sun goes down...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You'll need as much MEAT as you can get.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216230/extras/88149d2c814bb4bfa731458bc6b1bf5e.poster.avif?t=1771320063\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216230/extras/88149d2c814bb4bfa731458bc6b1bf5e.webm?t=1771320063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216230/extras/88149d2c814bb4bfa731458bc6b1bf5e.mp4?t=1771320063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the train tracks and you will find many monuments to explore and loot, the further you venture from the starting farm area, the better the loot you will find - but also the harder the enemies will become.   </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UPGRADE THE TRAIN</strong>  </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect <strong>SCRAP </strong>by breaking crates and destroying machines.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SCRAP</strong> can be used to repair and upgrade the train. There are a variety of upgrades to unlock which you will need to survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216230/extras/b3f35dafc81e4a30d99eb3c4f7d06bcf.poster.avif?t=1771320063\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216230/extras/b3f35dafc81e4a30d99eb3c4f7d06bcf.webm?t=1771320063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216230/extras/b3f35dafc81e4a30d99eb3c4f7d06bcf.mp4?t=1771320063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DEATH IS A REWARD, EARN CASH TO SPEND AT THE GUN SHOP</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Upon death, you earn MONEY</strong> for your Kill Count + Meat Collected + Scrap Collected during your run.<br>Money can be spent in the gun shop to <strong>unlock new weapons</strong> and <strong>gamble on a random weapon</strong> for your next run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216230/extras/fe393752e5f180b67ef643027b472b6e.poster.avif?t=1771320063\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216230/extras/fe393752e5f180b67ef643027b472b6e.webm?t=1771320063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3216230/extras/fe393752e5f180b67ef643027b472b6e.mp4?t=1771320063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DESTROY THE EVIL AI MEGAFACTORY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your mission is to destroy GRM (Global Resource Management): A rogue AI that poisoned the earth. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you manage to overcome the basics of surviving this world, you can attempt to penetrate the defenses of the factory and cleanse the planet of the evil AI virus.<br> </p>",
